item.title: Products
item.description: Find artificial intelligence enabled software for mental healthcare that you are looking for. Product description HoneyCube by HoneyNaps is a technology for mental disease prediction & bio-signal monitoring. Auticare is an XR-AI based Assistive Technology learning platform for Autism Spectrum Disorder(ASD) and special education. Genetika Plus uses data collected from blood samples to examine personal disorder profiles and responsiveness to a breadth of medications.
